My skin currently, is looking the best it's ever looked! I mean, spending some time in the sun and coming home with a gorgeous bronze glow does help 😂 However, since coming back, my skin got SO dry from this cold weather. I added a new step to my routine, cleansing my skin with Tatcha Deep cleanse and the @taoclean Aura Facia Cleaning Brush - gets rid of all the dry flaky bits of skin and leaves my skin so smooth and fresh! The UV light in the base kills 99% of acne causing bacteria! You can get the @taoclean brush here: https://bit.ly/2vHI8Re (AUS) http://bit.ly/2K5ASrK (US) use code 'HEIDI' to get the unit for only $49! #heidimakeupartist #collab #skincare #facial #clearskin #clean #selfcare #theartofclean #glowup #treatyoself #taoclean #uvlight #acnefree #blemishfree
